<Layout title="Privacy Policy – HiFi Studio & Mobile">
  <section class="prose mx-auto py-10">
    <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p>Last Updated: {new Date().toLocaleDateString()}</p>

    <p>
      This Privacy Policy explains how HiFi Studio & Mobile (“we”, “our”, or “us”) collects, uses, and protects your information when you use our website, services, blog, store, and WiFi registration platform.
    </p>

    <h2>Who We Are</h2>
    <p>
      HiFi Studio & Mobile is a proprietorship business based in 
      <strong>Ranior, Sirsa, Anandapur, Paschim Medinipur, 721260</strong>.
      We sell mobile devices, accessories, gadget services, technical support, and digital services.
    </p>

    <h2>Information We Collect</h2>

    <h3>1. Personal Information</h3>
    <ul>
      <li>Name</li>
      <li>Mobile Number</li>
      <li>Email (if provided)</li>
      <li>Billing & Payment Details (via Razorpay)</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>2. Device & Usage Information</h3>
    <ul>
      <li>IP Address</li>
      <li>Browser & device information</li>
      <li>Access logs (especially for WiFi access authentication)</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>3. Cookies & Third-Party Tracking</h3>
    <p>
      We use cookies to improve user experience. We also use:
    </p>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Google Analytics</strong> for usage tracking</li>
      <li><strong>Google AdSense</strong> for personalized advertisements</li>
    </ul>

    <p>
      Third-party vendors, including Google, use cookies to serve ads based on your interests.  
      You may opt-out of personalized advertising by visiting:  
      <a href="https://www.google.com/settings/ads">https://www.google.com/settings/ads</a>
    </p>

    <h2>Payments & Security (Razorpay)</h2>
    <p>
      We process online payments securely using <strong>Razorpay</strong>.  
      We do not store card numbers, UPI IDs, or bank login details.  
      All payment data is handled and encrypted directly by Razorpay.
    </p>

    <h2>How We Use Your Information</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>To process service registrations</li>
      <li>To verify WiFi or membership access</li>
      <li>To send important service updates</li>
      <li>To improve our services, blog, and website experience</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Data Sharing</h2>
    <p>
      We <strong>do not sell</strong> your data.  
      Data is only shared with:
    </p>
    <ul>
      <li>Razorpay (for payment processing)</li>
      <li>Google (Analytics & AdSense)</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Your Rights</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Request correction of your details</li>
      <li>Request deletion (if not required for security or billing)</li>
      <li>Opt-out of marketing communications</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Contact Us</h2>
    <p>
      If you have any privacy concerns, contact us at:
      <br><strong>Email:</strong> support@hifistudio.in
    </p>
  </section>
</Layout>
